== Installation ==

Requirements:
Python 2.6+
Git
crontab or other scheduling tool

Note: 'git' and 'python' commands should be in crontab's PATH

Copy gitmon.conf.example to ~/.gitmon.conf and edit it to your needs
Set up a crontab with your prefered timing, i.e: 

* */5 * * /path/to/gitmon > /tmp/gitmon.log

If you've done everything right, you should get some notifications.

